“You easy money for me but if you really sure you wanna do this, let's rock.” It seems like popular music artist Cassper Nyovest may be ready for another attention-grabbing boxing match with his new rival, popular rapper Priddy Ugly. The music pair got social media heated after hinting that there might be a possible boxing match between them. Both parties expressed that they are ready to lock horns, leaving many eagerly waiting for a date and place. This happens months after Cassper Nyovest had gotten into the ring with NaakMusiQ in a fight that had the country glued to their screens. Though the ‘’Good For That’’ hitmaker lost the fight, he still came off as ready and confident for another nail-biting boxing match. This will be Nyovest’s third fight after fighting controversial podcaster Slik Talk and NaakMusiQ. In a twitter spat that saw Cassper and Priddy Ugly claiming a spot on trends, Priddy told Nyovest that he was never scared to take him on. “Ek se Abhuti Billiato, I was never scared. You hit my line & called me up about a fight & I gladly said yes. I didn't hesitate, I didn't stutter. If you “ Iron Mike” for real, you can't be fighting people who can't fight. Seems to me like you are the scared one,” said Priddy. Nyovest responded: “I hope Priddy Ugly isn’t another one who is going to tweet & go hide in the studio like princess & ma drugs. Lol. He ouchea sounding very confident when he applying for a serious ass whooping. Could we possibly see #CassperNyovestvsPriddyUgly this year? It's about to get ugly.’’ Nyovest further pointed out that in terms of size, he is bigger than Priddy and he is ready to rock. “Size wise, I am way bigger than you, skill wise I am more experienced than you, You easy money for me but if you really sure you wanna do this, let's rock.”